      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="5431st">5431st meeting</inline>, on<docDate date="2006-04-28" refersTo="#adoptionDate">28 April 2006</docDate></docTitle>
